WARN Notices

Effective March 24, 2023: If you wish to receive further information about the most recent WARN Notice submitted to the Office of Workforce Development (OWD), sign up for our WARN Notice Mailing List. Submitted WARN Notices will be added to the list by the end of the next business day. WARN Notice updates will be emailed during business operating hours.

To receive any previous WARN Notices, submit an open records request to Kristin Stokely, General Counsel, at kristin.stokely@dhewd.mo.gov.
